361
00:20:08,160 --> 00:20:09,720
has anything to do with it.

362
00:20:14,280 --> 00:20:16,200
I know you'd protect them.

363
00:20:23,040 --> 00:20:24,720
Zhun is your son.

364
00:20:26,480 --> 00:20:28,600
