00:20:56,800 --> 00:20:58,000
Nanny Tao.

376
00:20:58,880 --> 00:21:00,560
Listen carefully.

377
00:21:01,280 --> 00:21:02,600
This woman

378
00:21:02,840 --> 00:21:05,120
