to His Majesty?

541
00:29:36,920 --> 00:29:38,160
Madam Xu,

542
00:29:38,640 --> 00:29:41,480
when can you bring that picture here?

543
00:29:41,720 --> 00:29:42,800
Eunuch Huang,

544
00:29:43,120 --> 00:29:44,080
actually the
"One Hundred Longevity Picture"

545
00:29:44,160 --> 00:29:45,960
