557
00:30:10,480 --> 00:30:12,600
Marquis, Madam Xu,

558
00:30:12,760 --> 00:30:14,520
excuse me for a moment.

559
00:30:14,640 --> 00:30:16,760
I'll go tell His Majesty right now.

560
00:30:16,800 --> 00:30:18,080
Thank you, Eunuch Huang.

